^PS(58.4,1,"VER",1,"SEG",1,"DAT",4,"DES",1,0)="Contains the Transaction Control Number of a transaction that initiated "
^PS(58.4,1,"VER",1,"SEG",1,"DAT",4,"DES",2,0)="the transaction. Required in response transaction only."
