^PS(58.4,1,"VER",8,"SEG",3,"DAT",1,"DES",9,0)="  02 Cancel/Void (Rx not picked up and returned to stock)"
^PS(58.4,1,"VER",8,"SEG",3,"DAT",1,"DES",10,0)="  03 Purged (Rx reported in error) (Available in 4.0 only)"
