^PS(58.4,1,"VER",10,"SEG",1,"DAT",5,"DES",3,0)="Note: Because historically there has been a noticeable amount of "
^PS(58.4,1,"VER",10,"SEG",1,"DAT",5,"DES",4,0)="extraneous information entered in this field, which has interfered with "
