^PS(58.4,1,"VER",12,"SEG",5,"DAT",4,"DES",1,0)="Code identifying the jurisdiction that issues the ID in PAT06. Used if "
^PS(58.4,1,"VER",12,"SEG",5,"DAT",4,"DES",2,0)="the PDMP requires such identification.  ASAP version 4.2b Standard "
^PS(58.4,1,"VER",12,"SEG",5,"DAT",4,"DES",3,0)="Appendix A lists jurisdictions."
