^PS(58.4,1,"VER",12,"SEG",5,"DAT",5,"DES",1,0)="Code to identify the type of ID in PAT06 if the PDMP requires a second "
^PS(58.4,1,"VER",12,"SEG",5,"DAT",5,"DES",2,0)="identifier. If PAT05 is used, PAT06 is required."
