^PS(58.4,1,"VER",13,"SEG",8,"DAT",9,"DES",3,0)="Note: The ASAP 4.2b Standard document uses the ""~"" in all examples. See "
^PS(58.4,1,"VER",13,"SEG",8,"DAT",9,"DES",4,0)="the ""Data Element Separators and Segment Terminators"" in the standard's "
