^PS(58.4,1,"VER",14,"SEG",5,"DAT",28,"DES",6,0)="Note: For additional fills per prescription, increment by 1. The second"
^PS(58.4,1,"VER",14,"SEG",5,"DAT",28,"DES",7,0)="partial fill would be reported as 02, up to a maximum of 99."
