^PS(58.4,1,"VER",15,"SEG",1,"DAT",4,"DES",2,0)="the transaction. Required in response transaction only."
^PS(58.4,1,"VER",15,"SEG",1,"DAT",4,"VAL",0)="^58.410111^1^1^3250319^^^"
