^PS(58.4,1,"VER",15,"SEG",6,"DAT",1,"DES",1,0)="Identifier assigned to the prescriber by CMS."
^PS(58.4,1,"VER",15,"SEG",6,"DAT",1,"DES",2,0)="Note: If the prescriber does not have a DEA number and prescribed a "
