^PS(58.4,1,"VER",15,"SEG",6,"DAT",2,"DES",2,0)="Enforcement Administration (DEA). Required when the prescription is for a "
^PS(58.4,1,"VER",15,"SEG",6,"DAT",2,"DES",3,0)="DEA-defined controlled substance."
