^PS(58.4,1,"VER",15,"SEG",7,"DAT",8,"DES",2,0)="Recommended way to report:"
^PS(58.4,1,"VER",15,"SEG",7,"DAT",8,"DES",3,0)="Report the patient's complete legal first name ONLY as listed on a "
